20for%20Spark%20drivers%20at%20some%20stores%20to%20reduce%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20he%20even%20gets%20there%2C%20a%20manager%20usually%20steps%20in%20first%20to%20ask%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20the%20receipt.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20mind%2C%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Sure%2C%20but%20also%2C%20why%20are%20you%20asking%20me%20that%3F'%26quot%3B%20the%20driver%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20asking%20me%20to%20show%20that%20I%20am%20not%20stealing%20items%20when%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20asked%20the%20same%20thing%20once%20I%20leave%20the%20store%20by%20the%20person%20at%20the%20door%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20is%20already%20on%20for%20gig%20delivery%20workers%20for%20services%20like%20Spark%2C%20Instacart%2C%20and%20DoorDash%2C%20who've%20got%20to%20get%20to%20a%20store%2C%20find%20exactly%20what%20customers%20ordered%2C%20and%20deliver%20it%20on%20time%20in%20hopes%20of%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-workers-call-out-customers-who-reduce-tips-by-marking-homes-tip-baiter-on-google-maps-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20tip%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20didn't%20expect%20there'd%20be%20another%20group%20of%20people%20they%20have%20to%20deal%20with%3A%20The%20store's%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20gig%20workers%20that%20BI%20spoke%20with%20said%20that%20cooperating%20%E2%80%94%20or%20fighting%20%E2%80%94%20with%20store%20workers%20is%20a%20regular%20part%20of%20their%20job%20as%20independent%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Instacart%20shopper%20who%20delivered%20from%20grocery%20stores%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon%2C%20last%20year%20told%20BI%20in%20February%20that%20employees%20at%20some%20stores%20would%20regularly%20follow%20him%20around%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20figured%20out%20that%20he%20was%20shopping%20for%20an%20order%20for%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20managers%20he%20confronted%20about%20the%20problem%20would%20tell%20him%20that%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20prevent%20theft%20%E2%80%94%20or%20simply%20tell%20him%20not%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20store%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20I%20would%20say%2C%20the%20very%20first%20thing%20that%20they%20would%20say%20is%2C%20'Oh%2C%20you're%20Instacart%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20shopper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Instacart%20spokesperson%20directed%20BI%20toward%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D5f940226e836a2cc8e08b194e350abc2e102b29ce18d65d092642841a3d39455%26postID%3D661fea2d97126ae3b20a517d%26postSlug%3Dgig-workers-fed-up-treated-badly-store-employees-instacart-walmart-2024-4%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.instacart.com%252Fhelp%252Fsection%252F4524023334676%252F360048057272%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunity%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20apply%20to%20shoppers%20as%20well%20as%20store%20workers.%20Among%20the%20guidelines%20is%20a%20request%20to%20%26quot%3Btreat%20others%20the%20way%20you%20want%20to%20be%20treated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20treats%20%26quot%3Bany%20reports%20of%20violations%20of%20these%20guidelines%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20Shoppers%20can%20report%20issues%20to%20Instacart's%20support%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Spark%20workers%20who%20go%20into%20a%20Walmart%20store%2C%20things%20can%20be%20even%20worse%20%E2%80%94%20ironic%2C%20some%20say%2C%20given%20Spark%20is%20owned%20and%20operated%20by%20Walmart.%20One%20former%20Spark%20driver%20in%20Montana%20told%20BI%20that%20store%20associates%20regularly%20ignored%20him%20when%20he%20needed%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20while%20he%20was%20waiting%20in%20line%20at%20a%20Walmart%20electronics%20department%20for%20some%20printer%20ink%20for%20a%20Spark%20order%2C%20an%20associate%20who%20recognized%20him%20simply%20moved%20on%20to%20the%20customer%20behind%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20motherf*cker%20can%20wait.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Spark%20drivers%20have%20said%20that%20associates%20have%20threatened%20to%20get%20their%20accounts%20deactivated%20when%20they%20push%20back%20on%20mistreatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20clear%20to%20the%20Walmart%20associates%20that%20I'm%20not%20a%20fellow%20employee%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20clear%20that%20I'm%20not%20a%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Spark%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20puts%20me%20in%20this%20weird%20gray%20area%20where%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20help%20me%20because%20I%20don't%20work%20with%20them%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20nice%20to%20me%20either%20because%20I'm%20not%20a%20customer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20founded%20as%20a%20values-driven%20company%20that%20is%20grounded%20in%20the%20four%20core%20values%20of%20Respect%2C%20Service%2C%20Excellence%2C%20and%20Integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Walmart%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWalmart%20associates%20are%20expected%20to%20operate%20based%20on%20these%20values%20and%20put%20fairness%2C%20equity%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20integrity%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20everything%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20Spark%20drivers%20who%20feel%20that%20they%20haven't%20been%20treated%20this%20way%20should%20contact%20Walmart's%20ethics%20complaint%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConflict%20between%20gig%20workers%20and%20store%20employees%20isn't%20new.%20Early%20in%20the%20pandemic%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhole-foods-employees-say-amazon-workers-cause-chaos-stores-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon's%20gig-worker%20shoppers%20became%20more%20common%20at%20Whole%20Foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20locations%2C%20sometimes%20drawing%20ire%20from%20store%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolden-age-gig-work-instacart-doordash-delivery-jobs-over-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGig%20delivery%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20had%20to%20contend%20with%20a%20range%20of%20challenges%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20from%20falling%20pay%20rates%20to%20greater%20competition%20for%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20store%20employees%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20giving%20gig%20workers%20a%20hard%20time.%20One%20Instacart%20shopper%20in%20Illinois%20told%20BI%20that%20they've%20had%20multiple%20customers%20claim%20that%20items%20are%20missing%20from%20orders%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20the%20shopper%20has%20taken%20photographs%20of%20the%20orders%20on%20the%20customers'%20doorstep%20to%20verify%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20Instacart%20assumes%20that%20the%20customer%20is%20right%2C%20the%20shopper%20said.%20That%20leaves%20shoppers%20with%20negative%20feedback%20and%20low%20ratings%20on%20their%20record%20%E2%80%94%20though%20this%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esomething%20that%20Instacart%20told%20BI%20doesn't%20affect%20the%20order%20offers%20that%20shoppers%20see%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Illinois%20shopper%20is%20skeptical%20of%20that%20explanation%2C%20telling%20BI%20that%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20also%20delivers%20for%20Instacart%2C%20often%20sees%20offers%20that%20she%20never%20gets.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20rating%20they%20gave%20you%2C%20the%20one%20star%20they%20gave%20you%2C%20plus%20their%20negative%20feedback%20that%20they%20left%20stays%20on%20your%20account%20for%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20shopper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20deliver%20food%2C%20groceries%2C%20or%20other%20items%20as%20a%20gig%20worker%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu