ida's%20culture%20war%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20he's%20found%20Floridians%20to%20be%20accepting%20and%20welcoming%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20David%20Maughan%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20human%20resource%20analyst%20who%20moved%20from%20Richmond%2C%20Virginia%2C%20to%20Oakland%20Park%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20August%202023%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20his%20boyfriend.%20He%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20about%20living%20in%20the%20Sunshine%20State%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cs%3EDavid%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cs%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fs%3EMy%20Florida%20story%20started%20in%202020%20when%20I%20met%20a%20guy%20named%20Brandon.%20We%20met%20online%2C%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20relationships%20nowadays%2C%20especially%20during%20early%20COVID.%20He%20lived%20in%20South%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Central%20Pennsylvania%20but%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Richmond%2C%20Virginia%2C%20since%20I%20was%20about%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandon%20and%20I%20dated%20casually%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20and%20then%20became%20official.%20We%20were%20long-distance%2C%20going%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20Virginia%20and%20Florida%20for%20about%20three%20years.%20We%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20together%20in%20the%20same%20place%2C%20so%20it%20became%20a%20question%20of%20which%20one%20of%20us%20would%20move.%20I%20work%20remotely%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20make%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20concerns%20about%20moving%20to%20Florida%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20move%20away%20from%20my%20entire%20support%20system.%20I'm%20part%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20and%20that%20was%20something%20I%20felt%20was%20really%20strong%20in%20Richmond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20starting%20over%20and%20making%20new%20friends%20in%20your%2030s%20is%20daunting.%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20be%20with%20my%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20I%20had%20met%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20so%20there%20would%20be%20a%20built-in%20friendship%20circle%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20but%20I%20still%20wanted%20to%20make%20my%20own%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20top%20two%20concerns%20were%20the%20state%20politics%20and%20the%20weather.%20Many%20of%20my%20Richmond%20friends%20understood%20the%20first%20but%20didn't%20get%20my%20concerns%20about%20the%20weather.%20Everyone%20says%20the%20weather%20in%20Florida%20is%20great%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20realize%20that%20Florida%20is%20%3Cem%3Ehot%20hot%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20the%20summer%2C%20it's%2090%20to%2095%20degrees%20every%20day.%20It's%20exhausting.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20outside.%20Some%20people%20love%20that.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Maughan%20poses%20for%20photos%20with%20his%20boyfriend%20Brandon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662027ba10c6b0cde5f0791e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Maughan%20and%20his%20boyfriend%20Brandon%20were%20long-distance%20for%20three%20years%20before%20David%20moved%20to%20Florida%20in%20August%202023.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%20Maughan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20primary%20concern%20I%20had%20was%20politics.%20I%20consider%20myself%20a%20progressive%20and%20a%20Democrat.%20I%20call%20myself%20a%20pragmatic%20progressive.%20In%20Richmond%2C%20I%20had%20been%20very%20involved%20in%20volunteering%20for%20local%20Democratic%20campaigns.%20It's%20more%20than%20just%20a%20hobby%20for%20me%3B%20it's%20something%20I'm%20really%20passionate%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20in%20progressive%20circles%20looks%20at%20Florida%20in%20horror%20because%20of%20what%2