0LGBTQ%2B%20adult%20sports%20league%20to%20participate%20in%2C%20and%20the%20nightlife%20nearby%20is%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20part%20of%20why%20it's%20been%20so%20easy%20to%20make%20friends%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-people-moving-florida-home-prices-cost-of-living-2023-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFlorida%2527s%2520population%2520jumped%2520by%25201.9%2C%2522hot%2520spots%2522%2520for%2520millennials.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20also%20transplants%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20haven't%20gotten%20any%20criticism%20from%20native%20Floridians%20about%20moving%20here.%20They've%20been%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20photo%20of%20David%20Maughan%20with%20his%20adult%20sports%20league%20and%20posing%20with%20his%20boyfriend%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6620267820b15f0ff428e790%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Maughan%20said%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20make%20friends%20in%20the%20Florida%20LGBTQ%20community%20by%20joining%20an%20adult%20sports%20league.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%20Maughan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20downsides%2C%20Florida%20has%20a%20really%20car-centric%20design%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20uncomfortable%20to%20get%20around%20any%20other%20way.%20There%20are%20six-lane%20roads%20with%20traffic%20flying%20down%20them.%20There%20are%20signs%20that%20say%20bikes%20can%20share%20the%20road%2C%20but%20you'd%20have%20to%20be%20insane%20to%20do%20that.%20Even%20biking%20to%20the%20beach%20is%20difficult.%20I%20think%20I've%20only%20been%20to%20the%20beach%20three%20times%20in%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20getting%20used%20to%20Florida's%20topography.%20Richmond%20is%20a%20place%20with%20hills%20and%20rivers.%20But%20here%2C%20it's%20obviously%20flat%20as%20