y%20have%20made%20significant%20strides%20in%20this%20direction.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnarendra-modi%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20starts%20his%20journey%20to%20his%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20let's%20examine%20how%20nationalism%20became%20the%20vehicle%20that%20conveyed%20to%20the%20BJP%20electoral%20support%20across%20religious%2C%20regional%2C%20and%20caste%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Colonial%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PM%20Modi%20began%20campaigning%20as%20the%20BJP's%20face%20in%202014%2C%20he%20understood%20well%20the%20emotive%20power%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20nationalism%2C%20and%20the%20windfall%20electoral%20gains%20that%20it%20can%20manifest.%20The%20power%20of%20nationalism%20at%20making%20or%20breaking%20government%20systems%20holds%20true%20across%20the%20world%20but%20is%20particularly%20keenly%20felt%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%20Blame%20it%20on%20the%20uneasy%20legacy%20of%20colonialism.%20Nehruvian%20ideals%20were%20a%20manifestation%20of%20nationalism%2C%20as%20was%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20endeavour%20to%20liberate%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20face%20of%20moral%20and%20material%20opposition%20from%20the%20Global%20West.%20The%20BJP%20was%20quick%20to%20make%20this%20playground%20its%20own%2C%20and%20slowly%20became%20the%20only%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20present%20context%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20-%20primarily%20the%20Congress%20-%20cannot%20be%20forgiven%20for%20ceding%20this%20space.%20When%20the%20BJP%20ratcheted%20its%20nationalism%20game%20up%2C%20the%20Opposition%20left%20the%20field%20on%20its%20ideological%20high%20horse.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20the%20BJP%20wanted%3A%20to%20be%20the%20only%20option.%20Every%20time%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felection-2024-why-pm-modi-and-the-bjp-are-so-confident-about-their-mission-400-5011284%5C%22%3ETINA%20(There%20Is%20No%20Alternative)%20factor%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20contemporary%20Indian%20politics%20is%20invoked%2C%20the%20BJP%20gloats%20a%20little%20more%20and%20probably%20laughs%20at%20the%20willing%20suspension%20of%20disbelief%20on%20its%20opponent's%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TINA%20factor%20exists%20not%20because%20there%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20capable%20politicians%20in%20the%20Opposition%20but%20due%20to%20their%20lack%20of%20preparation%20in%20challenging%20the%20BJP%20juggernaut.%20Politics%20is%20a%20game%20where%20the%20opponent%20is%20met%20with%20and%20defeated%20on%20a%20common%20ground.%20The%20moment%20the%20Opposition%20decided%20to%20exit%20the%20field%20of%20nationalism%2C%20they%20lost%20the%20game.%20Banishing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnationalism-is-not-an-option-requires-100-per-cent-commitment-jagdeep-dhankhar-5205687%5C%22%3Enationalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20their%20political%20imaginary%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Opposition%20that%20has%20strengthened%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Voter%20And%20The%20Real%20Import%20Of%20'Vikas'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorruption%2C%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%20et%20al%20have%20been%20any%20electorate's%20refrain%20since%20independence.%20Political%20parties%20may%20go%20on%20pretending%20that%20elections%20are%20won%20or%20lost%20over%20these%20'issues'%2C%20but%20they%20know%20that%20it's%20not%20the%20case.%20All%20politicians%20would%20be%20getting%20their%20hands%20dirty%20in%20development%20work%20in%20their%20constituencies%20if%20that%20were%20indeed%20the%20reality.%20The%20Indian%20voter%20is%20quick%20to%20punish%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20it%20but%20does%20not%20necessarily%20reward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsabka-saath-sabka-vikas-sabka-vishwas-is-bjps-mantra-pm-modi-2375939%5C%22%3E'Vikas'%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20political%20parties%20begin%20to%20take%20the%20voter%20for%20granted%2C%20they%20are%20shown%20the%20door%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20keeps%20India's%20democracy-however%20fallible-dynamic%20and%20vibrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20Indians%2C%20the%20vote%20is%20still%20an%20emotive%20issue.%20It%20is%20pointless%2C%20often%20counterproductive%2C%20to%20chide%20them%20for%20not%20making%20the%20'correct'%20choice.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20been%20making%20this%20mistake%20at%20least%20since%202014.%20When%20will%20it%20learn%20that%20guilt-tripping%20the%20voter%20does%20not%20change%20electoral%20fortunes%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20elections%20offer%20clear%20lessons.%20The%20BJP%20has%20lost%20states%20where%20murmurs%20of%20dissatisfaction%20over%20in-fighting%2C%20poor%20governance%20and%20overt%20corruption%20have%20not%20been%20drowned%20by%20loud%20rhetoric.%20Hard%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Opposition%20has%20paid%20off%20there.%20Regional%20parties%2C%20like%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20have%20been%20far%20more%20prescient%20in%20tackling%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20own%20terms.%20They%20have%20learnt%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20and%20are%20not%20ceding%20any%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20Has%20Failed%20To%20Reclaim%20Space%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20democracy%2C%20in%20institutional%20terms%2C%20has%20been%20evolving%20since%20independence%2C%20continuously%20growing%20wider%20and%20deeper.%20What%20Alexis%20Tocqueville%20said%20of%20American%20democracy%20can%20be%20easily%20applied%20to%20the%20Indian%20context%3A%20democracy%20is%20a%20socio-cultural%20tendency.%20It%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20a%20little%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20socio-cultural%20tendency%20is%20left%20only%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20That%20the%20BJP%20can%20casually%20fling%20accusations%20like%20'anti-national'%20or%20'%3Cem%3Edesh%20ke%20gaddaar%3C%2Fem%3E'%20at%20its%20critics%20is%20also%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20some%20measure.%20Was%20bunching%20in%20the%20furthest%20Left%20corner%20while%20the%20Right-wing%20politics%20occupied%20the%20centre%20stage%20expedient%3F%20Why%20could%20they%20not%20stand%20firm%20on%20this%20ground%20in%20the%20middle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndermining%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20use%20of%20a%20cocktail%20of%20nationalism's%20emotional%20appeal%20and%20ruthless%20electoral%20pragmatism%20has%20cost%20the%20Opposition%20two%20elections.%20Whether%202024%20will%20be%20any%20different%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20A%20functional%20democratic%20nation%20needs%20a%20strong%20government%20and%20an%20equally%20strong%20Opposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713597660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fu1lj7k0s_tiranga-rally-srinagar_625x300_25_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnationalism-in-elections-bjp-understands-opposition-still-doesnt-5483085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20the%20BJP%20ratcheted%20its%20nationalism%20game%20up%2C%20the%20Opposition%20left%20the%20field%20on%20its%20ideological%20high%20horse.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20-%20to%20be%20the%20only%20option.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnationalism-in-elections-bjp-understands-opposition-still-doesnt-5483085%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Decoding%20Dubai%20Flash%20Floods%3A%20Experts%20Say%20Climate%20Change%20Has%20Clear%20Ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20heavy%20rains%20that%20flooded%20Dubai%20this%20week%20halted%20air%20traffic%2C%20damaged%20buildings%20and%20streets%20-%20and%20left%20climate%20experts%20and%20common%20citizens%20asking%20whether%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20hottest%20and%20driest%20cities%20should%20be%20better%20prepared%20for%20extreme%20storms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeather%20forecasters%20knew%20days%20in%20advance%20that%20a%20major%20storm%20was%20heading%20for%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20authorities%20issued%20warnings%20asking%20citizens%20to%20stay%20home.%20Yet%20its%20largest%20city%20Dubai%20was%20still%20brought%20to%20a%20halt%20this%20week%2C%20with%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20rain%20events%20in%20decades%20flooding%20streets%2C%20homes%20and%20highways.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStormwater%20management%20systems%20were%20historically%20deemed%20an%20'unnecessary%20cost'%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20rainfall%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20said%20Karim%20Elgendy%2C%20an%20associate%20fellow%20at%20the%20Environment%20and%20Society%20Centre%20at%20Chatham%20House.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20variability%20of%20rainfall%20increases%20across%20the%20region%20and%20as%20the%20likelihood%20of%20such%20events%20rises%2C%20the%20economic%20case%20for%20such%20systems%20becomes%20stronger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman-caused%20climate%20change%20is%20making%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20heat%20and%20rain%20more%20intense%2C%20frequent%20and%20harder%20to%20predict.%20The%20Middle%20East%20is%20forecast%20to%20face%20higher%20temperatures%20and%20a%20decline%20in%20overall%20rainfall%2C%20according%20to%20long-term%20scientific%20projections.%20But%20these%20very%20arid%20places%20will%20also%20experience%20storms%20that%20drop%20unprecedented%20rain%2C%20according%20to%20researchers.%20That's%20forcing%20governments%20to%20consider%20whether%20to%20adapt%20to%20rare%20but%20destructive%20events%20-%20and%20how.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20UAE%20government%20didn't%20immediately%20reply%20to%20a%20written%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20real%20tradeoff%20in%20thinking%20about%20the%20cost%20and%20the%20opportunity%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Linda%20Shi%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20specializing%20in%20urban%20climate%20adaptation%20at%20Cornell%20University%20in%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BThese%20events%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20erratic%20and%20unpredictable.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20battered%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20its%20heaviest%20downpour%20since%20records%20began%20in%201949.%20Scientists%20and%20weather%20forecasters%20attribute%20the%20storm%20to%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20moisture%20rising%20from%20warming%20seas%20to%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20before%20falling%20as%20rain%20over%20to%20the%20Arabian%20Peninsula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEl%20Nino%2C%20the%20climate%20phenomenon%20that%20makes%20seas%20warmer%20and%20alters%20weather%20patterns%20globally%2C%20may%20have%20affected%20the%20storm.%20Climate%20change%20can't%20be%20ruled%20out%20as%20a%20factor%2C%20though%20more%20detailed%20studies%20are%20needed%20to%20establish%20its%20exact%20influence%2C%20several%20climatologists%20and%20forecasters%20told%20Bloomberg%20Green.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20massive%20floods%20like%20this%20have%20occurred%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20huge%20scale%20and%20intensity%20of%20the%20rainfall%20that%20caused%20it%20are%20exactly%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20more%20of%20in%20our%20warmer%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hannah%20Cloke%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20hydrology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Reading%20in%20the%20UK.%20%26quot%3BWith%20so%20much%20rain%20falling%20all%20at%20once%2C%20even%20carefully%20designed%20drainage%20systems%20will%20struggle%20to%20cope.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20floods%20drew%20immediate%20attention%20to%20the%20UAE's%20cloud-seeding%20program%2C%20which%20involves%20injecting%20particles%20into%20clouds%20that%20can%20influence%20rainfall.%20But%20it%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20data%20analysis%26quot%3B%20to%20ascertain%20the%20role%2C%20if%20any%2C%20it%20played%20in%20making%20the%20rains%20more%20extreme%2C%20according%20to%20Auroop%20Ganguly%2C%20a%20civil%20and%20environmental%20engineering%20professor%20at%20Northeastern%20University%20in%20Boston.%20%26quot%3BOften%20major%20floods%20in%20a%20city%20relate%20to%20urban%20drainage%20and%20related%20infrastructures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubai%20and%20the%20UAE%20more%20broadly%20were%20unprepared%20for%20such%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20water%20falling%20over%20such%20a%20short%20period.%20Drainage%20systems%20quickly%20proved%20insufficient%20to%20absorb%20the%20deluge.%20Underground%20garages%20completely%20flooded%2C%20with%20water%20flowing%20into%20streets%2C%20highways%20and%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETankers%20were%20deployed%20to%20pump%20water%20from%20streets%20once%20the%20storm%20passed%2C%20but%20some%20communities%2C%20lakes%20and%20local%20football%20grounds%20remained%20waterlogged%20days%20later.%20The%20impacts%20continue%20to%20ripple%20outward.%20Shelves%20in%20some%20local%20supermarkets%20were%20still%20empty%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%20Schools%20were%20shut%20for%20four%20days%20and%20government%20employees%20were%20asked%20to%20work%20from%20home%20where%20possible.%20Dubai's%20international%20airport%20said%20Friday%20afternoon%20it%20was%20allowing%20departures%20to%20operate%20but%20it%20was%20limiting%20the%20number%20of%20inbound%20flights%20for%20the%20next%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCities%20in%20arid%20regions%20may%20be%20especially%20ill-prepared%20for%20heavy%20rain%20events%20because%20buildings%2C%20landscapes%20and%20infrastructure%20have%20not%20been%20designed%20with%20drainage%20capacity%20as%20a%20primary%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zachary%20Lamb%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20City%20and%20Regional%20Planning%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20at%20Berkeley%20in%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BClimate%20change%20is%20unsettling%20long-held%20assumptions%20about%20landscape%20and%20climate%20conditions%20that%20have%20informed%20the%20design%20and%20planning%20of%20buildings%20and%20cities%20for%20generations.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubai%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20facing%20that%20problem.%20Last%20year%2C%20a%20superstorm%20burst%20dams%20in%20Libya%2C%20causing%20floods%20that%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Derna%20and%20killed%20at%20least%205%2C000%20people.%20Parts%20of%20Beijing%20were%20also%20submerged%20last%20year%20after%20the%20Chinese%20capital%20was%20battered%20by%20the%20heaviest%20rainfall%20in%20140%20years%20of%20weather%20records.%20The%20flooding%20washed%20away%20homes%20and%20caused%20dozens%20of%20fatalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDubai%20can%20only%20prepare%20for%20what%20it%20sees%20as%20being%20within%20the%20range%20of%20probability%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lisa%20Dale%2C%20a%20climate%20adaptation%20specialist%20at%20Columbia%20University%20in%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BPredictions%20for%20future%20weather%20patterns%20foundationally%20rely%20on%20past%20weather%20patterns%2C%20leaving%20many%20governments%20unprepared%20for%20climate%20change%20impacts%20that%20are%20not%20historically%20common.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713597600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnfk3r3mo_dubai-floods_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdubai-floods-expose-weaknesses-to-a-rapidly-changing-climate-5482872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20heavy%20rains%20that%20flooded%20Dubai%20this%20week%20halted%20air%20traffic%2C%20damaged%20buildings%20and%20streets%20-%20and%20left%20climate%20experts%20and%20common%20citizens%20asking%20whether%20one