%20like%20this.%20I%20feel%20that%20this%20problem%20of%20Love%20Jihad%20is%20spreading%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gang%20had%20conspired%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20They%20had%20planned%20either%20to%20trap%20her%20or%20to%20execute%20her.%20They%20have%20been%20threatening%20her%20in%20that%20backdrop.%20However%2C%20the%20girl%20did%20not%20heed%20to%20their%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hiremath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20the%20lead%20accused%20and%20an%20investigation%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20protests%20rage%20across%20the%20state%20seeking%20strict%20punishment%20for%20Fayaz%2C%20his%20mother%20sought%20forgiveness%20and%20said%20that%20what%20her%20son%20did%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20my%20son%2C%20I%20seek%20forgiveness%20from%20all%20people%20of%20Karnataka.%20I%20seek%20forgiveness%20from%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20girl%20as%20well.%20She%20is%20also%20like%20my%20daughter.%20I%20am%20not%20differentiating%20here%20at%20all.%20I%20know%20how%20they%20must%20be%20grieving.%20I%20am%20equally%20sorrowful.%C2%A0%20What%20my%20son%20did%20is%20wrong.%20No%20matter%20who%20it%20is%2C%20what%20is%20done%20is%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Mumtaz%2C%20Fayaz's%20mother%2C%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnNeha%20Hiremath%2C%20daughter%20of%20Congress%20corporator%20Niranjan%20Hiremath%2C%20was%20a%20first-year%20Master%20of%20Computer%20Applications%20student%20at%20the%20BV%20Bhoomaraddi%20College%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%20in%20Hubballi.%20Officials%20said%20she%20had%20known%20her%20attacker%2C%20Fayaz%20-%20who%20also%20studied%20with%20her%20at%20the%20college%2C%20but%20later%20dropped%20out%20-%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%205%20pm%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Neha%20was%20walking%20inside%20the%20campus%20when%20Fayaz%20confronted%20her.%20CCTV%20footage%20shows%20a%20couple%20of%20sentences%20being%20exchanged%20between%20them%20before%20Fayaz%20attacks%20her.%20Neha%20falls%20to%20the%20ground%20after%20being%20stabbed%20the%20first%20time%20and%20Fayaz%20goes%20on%20to%20knife%20her%20at%20least%20six%20more%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFayaz%20then%20makes%20a%20run%20for%20it%20while%20some%20students%20chase%20after%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713597540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffck06jrg_neha-hiremath_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-murder-accuseds-mother-apologises-amid-love-jihad-allegations-5482966%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Massive%20protests%20have%20broken%20out%20across%20Karnataka%20after%20a%20Congress%20corporator's%20daughter%20was%20stabbed%20to%20death%20in%20an%20alleged%20unsuccessful%20attempt%20of%20'love%20jihad'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-murder-accuseds-mother-apologises-amid-love-jihad-allegations-5482966%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-murder-accuseds-mother-apologises-amid-love-jihad-allegations-5482966%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-murder-accuseds-mother-apologises-amid-love-jihad-allegations-5482966%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Soo%20Hyun%20and%20Kim%20Ji%20Won%20get%20mushy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713597291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109453419%2Cimgsize-50372.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fkim-soo-hyun-plans-romantic-christmas-surprise-for-kim-ji-won-in-queen-of-tears%2Farticleshow%2F109453424.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109453424.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBaek%20Hyun%20Woo%20surprises%20Hong%20Hae%20In%20with%20a%20magical%20early%20Christmas%20celebration%20at%20Queens%20Department%20Store%2C%20showcasing%20a%20romantic%20gesture%20amidst%20twinkling%20lights%20and%20snowfall%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20heartwarming%20moment%20in%20the%20upcoming%20episode%20of%20'Queen%20of%20Tears'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Amethi%2C%20Congress's%20%26quot%3BSahabzade%26quot%3B%20Will%20Lose%20Wayanad%20Seat%20Too%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20saying%20that%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress's%20sahabzade%26quot%3B%20will%20also%20lose%20from%20Wayanad%20constituency%20in%20Kerala%20and%20he%20will%20have%20to%20look%20for%20a%20safer%20seat%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20at%20Nanded%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20campaign%20for%20BJP%20candidates%20from%20Nanded%20and%20Hingoli%20seats%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20information%20available%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20indicates%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20one-sided%20voting%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20losing%20Amethi%2C%20the%20Congress'%20sahabzade%20will%20lose%20Wayanad%20as%20well.%20So%20he%20will%20have%20to%20look%20for%20a%20safe%20seat%20after%20April%2026.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20said%20some%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders%20left%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20as%20they%20have%20no%20courage%20to%20contest%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20family%20will%20not%20vote%20for%20a%20Congress%20candidate%20in%20the%20constituency%20where%20they%20live%20as%20there%20is%20no%20party%20candidate%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20he%20has%20spent%2010%20years%20fixing%20the%20bad%20governance%20of%20the%20Congress%20regimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20work%20needs%20to%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20a%20barrier%20in%20the%20development%20of%20farmers%20and%20poor%20people%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agriculture%20crisis%20did%20not%20happen%20now.%20It%20happened%20because%20of%20the%20flawed%20policies%20of%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20he%20said%20it%20has%20no%20face%20to%20project%20and%20people%20do%20not%20know%20whom%20to%20entrust%20the%20country's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20may%20claim%20anything%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20accepted%20defeat%20even%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20termed%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20a%20grouping%20of%20selfish%20people%20who%20have%20come%20together%20to%20protect%20their%20corrupt%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20voters%20to%20come%20out%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20exercise%20their%20voting%20right%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20not%20doing%20any%20favour%20by%20voting.%20you%20are%20securing%20the%20country's%20future.%20I%20want%20to%20boost%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20party%20workers%20from%20the%20opposition.%20You%20(opposition%20leaders)%20are%20sure%20to%20lose%20the%20polls%2C%20but%20you%20will%20get%20a%20chance%20some%20day.%20But%20you%20must%20appeal%20to%20voters%20to%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%