C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20(28%20off%209)%20went%20on%20a%20six-hitting%20spree%20to%20take%20CSK%20to%20a%20fighting%20176%20for%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalfway%20stage%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20happy%20with%20160.%20Felt%20the%20wicket%20was%20slow%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20grip%20but%20not%20too%20much.%20160-165%20would%20have%20been%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20MSD%20walks%20in%20and%20the%20bowlers%20feel%20intimidated.%20He%20walks%20in%20and%20bowlers%20were%20under%20pressure%2C%20the%20crowd%20was%20really%20loud%2C%20he%20has%20done%20it%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20177%2C%20Rahul%20(82)%20and%20De%20Kock%20(54)%20batted%20with%20authority%20during%20their%20match-winning%20alliance%20of%20134%2C%20the%20highest%20partnership%20for%20any%20wicket%20at%20the%20Ekana%20Stadium%2C%20as%20LSG%20scored%20180%20for%202%20in%2019%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFelt%20that%20if%20we%20bat%20well%2C%20we%20could%20chase%20it%20down.%20I%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20and%20today%20it%20came%20off.%20With%20Chennai's%20spinners%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20put%20brakes%20on%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20to%20get%20to%20a%20good%20start.%20Tried%20to%20take%20them%20down%2C%20luckily%20it%20came%20off.%20When%20your%20partnership%20goes%20on%2C%20you%20can%20take%20a%20few%20more%20chances.%20Glad%20that%20it%20happened.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108591-ruturaj-gaikwad-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERuturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CSK%20captain%2C%20said%20his%20team%20was%2010-15%20runs%20short%20with%20dew%20coming%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20finished%20off%20very%20well%2C%20couldn't%20have%20asked%20for%20more.%20But%20after%20powerplay%2C%20we%20couldn't%20kick%20on%20till%2014-15th%20over.%20We%20lost%20wickets%20regularly%20and%20were%2010-15%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSlightly%20difficult%20to%20bat%20but%20with%20Impact%20Player%20rule%20you%20need%20an%20extra%20batter.%20With%20dew%20coming%20on%20later%2C%20felt%20180-190%20could%20have%20been%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20bowlers%20couldn't%20produce%20a%20breakthrough%20as%20Rahul%20and%20De%20Kock%20batted%20well%20in%20the%20powerplay%20and%20Gaikwad%20agreed%20they%20needed%20to%20bowl%20better%20in%20the%20first%20six%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BBowling%20in%20the%20powerplay%5D%20is%20one%20area%20we%20would%20like%20to%20improve%2C%20puts%20opposition%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20if%20we%20can%20get%20wickets%20in%20the%20powerplay.%20Good%20to%20play%20them%20again%20soon%2C%20will%20come%20back%20with%20homework%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20teams%20will%20again%20face%20off%20on%20April%2023%20at%20Chepauk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713594720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjrk0l97g_ms-dhoni_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fbowlers-intimidated-crowd-loud-on-ms-dhoni-storm-in-lucknow-kl-rahuls-huge-statement-5480532%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20had%20a%20good%20day%20in%20office%20as%20he%20was%20spot-on%20with%20his%20bowling%20changes%20and%20also%20took%20two%20catches%20and%20affected%20a%20stumping%20before%20returning%20to%20smash%20a%20match-winning%2053-ball%2082%20to%20boot%20with.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vidya%20Balan%20opens%20up%20on%20privacy%20in%20marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713594705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109452535%2Cim