quot%3B%20The%20final%20challenge%C2%A0ultimately%20ends%20in%20asking%20the%20user%20to%20kill%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20are%20often%20forced%20into%20completing%20these%20tasks%20through%20threats%2C%20blackmail%2C%20or%20psychological%20manipulation.%20The%20game's%20name%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20behaviour%20of%20blue%20whales%2C%20which%20are%20known%20to%20beach%20themselves%20intentionally%2C%20which%20often%20results%20in%20the%20death%20of%20the%20whale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20reports%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Whale%20Challenge%26quot%3B%20being%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20hundreds%20of%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20spread%20from%20Russia%20to%20other%20countries%20like%20Ukraine%2C%20India%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20of%20the%20Blue%20Whale%20Challenge%20traces%20back%20to%20the%20tragic%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fblogs-trending-46505722%C2%A0%5C%22%3ERina%20Palenkova%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20November%2022%2C%202015%2C%20Ms%20Palenkova%2C%20a%20teenage%20girl%20from%20Russia%20posted%20a%20selfie%20online.%20In%20the%20photo%2C%20she%20stands%20outdoors%20with%20a%20black%20scarf%20hiding%20her%20mouth%20and%20nose%2C%20while%20showing%20off%20her%20middle%20finger%2C%20which%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20coated%20with%20dried%20blood.%20The%20caption%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BNya%20bye.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Palenkova%20died%20by%20suicide%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713593220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8g0pqq0o_tee_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-students-death-in-us-brings-back-concerns-about-blue-whale-game-challenge-5482294%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20believed%20the%2020-year-old%20was%20playing%20the%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Whale%20Challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20online%20game%20which%20has%20also%20