%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERajkummar%20Rao%20dismisses%20plastic%20surgery%20rumors%2C%20attributing%20his%20changed%20appearance%20to%20weight%20loss%20and%20a%20minor%20chin%20filler%20procedure%20advised%20by%20his%20dermatologist%20for%20facial%20balance.%20He%20emphasizes%20his%20commitment%20to%20fitness%20and%20asserts%20confidence%20in%20his%20appearance%2C%20debunking%20the%20notion%20of%20extensive%20plastic%20surgery.%20Rajkummar%20ill%20now%20be%20seen%20in%20Srikant%20Bolla's%20biopic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jigar%20Shah%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBumrah%20Had%20PBKS%20On%20Back%20Foot%26quot%3B%3A%20IPL%20Winning%20Coach%20Slams%20Hardik's%20Captaincy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Australian%20all-rounder%20Tom%20Moody%20feels%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20did%20not%20use%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20optimally%20during%20the%20IPL%20clash%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20which%20allowed%20them%20to%20fight%20back%20from%20a%20difficult%20position%20and%20come%20within%20touching%20distance%20of%20MI's%20total.%20Bumrah%20was%20matchless%20in%20the%20game%20in%20Mullanpur%20on%20Thursday%2C%20taking%20the%20wickets%20of%20opener%20Sam%20Curran%2C%20Rilee%20Rossouw%20and%20the%20dangerous%20Shashank%20Singh%20to%20help%20MI%20win%20by%20nine%20runs.%20MI%20had%20set%20PBKS%20a%20target%20of%20193.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20mainstay%20bagged%20two%20wickets%20in%20the%20second%20over%2C%20dismissing%20Curran%20and%20Rossouw%2C%20but%20just%20when%20PBKS%20looked%20down%20and%20out%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20allowing%20the%20home%20team%20to%20claw%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20Mumbai%20leaning%20on%20him%20so%20much%20to%20turn%20their%20fortunes%20around.%20He%20bowled%20two%20overs%20early%20on%20and%20had%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20on%20their%20back.%20But%2C%20interestingly%20enough%2C%20he%20didn't%20bowl%20another%20over%20until%20the%2013th%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20Australian%20cricketer%20on%20Star%20Sports%20Cricket%20Live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20powers%20at%20the%20moment.%20And%20that's%20my%20point%20of%20where%20I%20think%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20let%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20back%20into%20this%20contest.%20(Gerald)%20Coetzee%20and%20Bumrah%20for%20mine%2C%20and%20I'll%20be%20interested%20to%20hear%20what%20the%20other%20fast%20bowlers%20think%20on%20this%20show.%20Should%20(Bumrah)%20have%20bowled%20again%20to%20be%20able%20to%20put%20Punjab%20completely%20out%20onto%20the%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20South%20African%20quick%20Dale%20Steyn%20opined%20that%20MI's%20frontline%20pacers%20Bumrah%20and%20Coetzee%20need%20support%20from%20other%20bowlers%2C%20given%20the%20rigours%20of%20the%20IPL.%20He%20hinted%20that%20an%20off-colour%20Pandya%20was%20not%20helping%20MI's%20bowling%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20see%20them%20(MI)%20close%20out%20games%20early%20by%20bringing%20Bumrah%20back%20or%20Coetzee.%20But%20then%20they%20have%20to%20depend%20on%20guys%20like%20Hardik%20to%20finish%20off%2C%20who%20hasn't%20been%20bowling%20as%20well%20of%20late%20and%20some%20of%20the%20other%20bowlers%20travelling%20like%20(Romario)%20Shepherd%2C%20they%20may%20struggle%20in%20the%20back%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMumbai%20are%20in%20a%20situation%20now%20where%20they%20have%20to%20tactically%20figure%20things%20out%2C%20but%20they%20also%20need%20somebody%20to%20step%20up%2C%20their%20bowlers%20to%20step%20up%20and%20really%20help%20out%20Bumrah%20and%20Coetzee%2C%20because%20if%20they%20(MI)%20keep%20going%20the%20way%20they%20are%2C%20they%20might%20lose%20more%20points%20again.%26quot%3B%20Moody%20also%20felt%20that%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20will%20have%20to%20play%20the%20entire%20du