%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDozens%20search%20near%20Mexico%20City%20garbage%20dump%20independently%2C%20facing%20risks%20and%20lack%20of%20official%20support.%20Collectives%20emphasize%20collective%20action%2C%20volunteers%20use%20tools%20to%20sift%20through%20waste.%20Criticism%20continues%20about%20the%20administration's%20handling%20of%20missing%20persons'%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsearch-for-missing-loved-ones-volunteers-rally-against-indifference-in-mexico%2Farticleshow%2F109450225.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsearch-for-missing-loved-ones-volunteers-rally-against-indifference-in-mexico%2Famp_articleshow%2F109450225.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsearch-for-missing-loved-ones-volunteers-rally-against-indifference-in-mexico%2Famp_articleshow%2F109450225.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBJP's%20'400-Paar'%20Film%20Flopped%20On%20Day%201%20Of%20Polls%26quot%3B%3A%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3B400%20paar%26quot%3B%20film%20has%20become%20super%20flop%20on%20the%20first%20day%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Mahagathbandhan%20is%20winning%20all%20four%20seats%20in%20the%20first%20phase.%20We%20have%20held%20block-wise%20meetings%20and%20the%20feedback%20has%20been%20very%20good.%20The%20BJP's%20%26quot%3B400%20paar%26quot%3B%20film%20has%20become%20a%20super%20flop%20on%20the%20first%20day%20itself.%20The%20people%20of%20Bihar%20are%20aware%20and%20will%20teach%20them%20a%20lesson%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20told%20ANI%20that%20there%20is%20no%20competition%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20as%20Bihar%20will%20give%20shocking%20results%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20competition%20in%20the%20first%20phase.%20We%20have%20said%20many%20times%20before%20Bihar%20will%20give%20shocking%20results%20this%20time.%20They%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar.%20The%20promises%20made%20by%20Modi%20ji%20in%202014%20and%202019%20were%20not%20fulfilled.%20Now%2C%20the%20public%20is%20tired%20of%20their%20statements%20and%20false%20promises.%20We%20have%20promised%20that%20we%20will%20give%20a%20special%20package%20to%20Bihar%20along%20with%20special%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20local%20issues%20hold%20the%20key%20in%20these%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Mahagathbandhan%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20are%20working%20together.%20Unemployment%20is%20the%20biggest%20issue%20in%20Bihar%2C%20besides%20inflation%2C%20poverty%2C%20and%20investment.%20Migration%20and%20floods%20are%20also%20issues.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20very%20worried.%20They%20say%20they%20will%20abolish%20the%20Constitution.%20Those%20who%20destroy%20the%20Constitution%20will%20themselves%20be%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20Bihar%20recorded%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2048.88%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20voting.%20Four%20seats%20-%20Jamui%2C%20Nawada%2C%20Gaya%2C%20and%20Aurangabad%20-%20had%20gone%20to%20polls%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20also%20comprising%20the%20JDU%20and%20LJP%2C%20had%20secured%2039%20out%20of%2040%20seats%20while%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20managed%20to%20win%20just%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C