20what's%20called%20a%20Sandoval%20hearing%2C%20where%20his%20lawyers%20and%20prosecutors%20argued%20over%20what%20%26quot%3Bprior%20bad%20acts%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20fair%20game%20on%20his%20cross-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20visibly%20angry%20%E2%80%94%20scowling%20at%20the%20defense%20table%20%E2%80%94%20as%20his%20acts%20were%20sorted%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20courtroom%2C%20he%20thumped%20a%20wooden%20railing%20with%20his%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20object%20to%20each%2C%26quot%3B%20defense%20lawyer%20Emil%20Bove%20had%20said%20of%20all%20the%20acts%20prosecutors%20want%20to%20bring%20into%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20nearly%20two-hour%20Sandoval%20hearing%2C%20Bove%20complained%20of%20the%20DA's%20plans%20to%20the%20trial%20judge%2C%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBove%20said%20that%20the%20verdicts%2C%20judgments%2C%20and%20contempt-of-court%20orders%20that%20prosecutors%20want%20to%20question%20Trump%20about%20are%20mostly%20under%20appeal%20and%20%26quot%3Bunduly%20prejudicial%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20they'd%20unfairly%20prejudice%20the%20jury%20against%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20lawyer%20fought%20especially%20hard%20against%20jurors%20hearing%20that%20a%20federal%20jury%20in%20Manhattan%20had%20found%20Trump%20liable%20for%20violating%20Carroll%20with%20his%20hands%20during%20an%20assault%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%20%E2%80%94%20an%20attack%20that%20the%20judge%20said%20effectively%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-rape-e-jean-carroll-sexual-abuse-jury-judge-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20amounted%20to%20rape.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20theory%20of%20this%20trial%3F%26quot%3B%20Bove%20asked%20angrily.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20they%20making%20arguments%20about%20sexual%20misconduct%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20demanded.%20%26quot%3BThis