er%20lesson%20plans%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJean-Baptiste%20writes%20in%20her%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20think%20side-hustling%20requires%20new%20skills%20and%20it%20doesn't.%20Look%20at%20what%20you%20are%20already%20doing%20and%20expand%20that%20into%20a%20side%20hustle.%20At%20the%20height%20of%20my%20lesson%20plan-selling%20era%2C%20I%20had%20forty%20to%20sixty%20assets%20in%20my%20digital%20store%20and%20was%20making%20%2410%2C000%20to%20%2412%2C000%20a%20year.%20This%20allowed%20me%20to%20use%20my%20teacher%20check%20for%20expenses%20and%20saving%2C%20while%20the%20side-hustle%20money%20went%20to%20my%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reason%20many%20side%20hustles%20fail%20is%20that%20they're%20outside%20your%20skill%20set%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20the%20startup%20phase%20more%20difficult.%20%26quot%3BYour%20side%20hustle%20will%20only%20thrive%20if%20it%20fits%20your%20skills%20and%20lifestyle%20criteria%2C%20%5Bso%5D%20look%20and%20see%20what%20you%20are%20already%20doing%20and%20start%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Jean-Baptiste%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDetermine%20your%20ROI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20seek%20to%20increase%20your%20income%20streams%2C%20ask%20yourself%3A%20What%20is%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Froi%5C%22%3Ereturn%20on%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Jean-Baptiste%20advises%2C%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you've%20taken%20the%20time%20to%20assess%20your%20skills%20and%20outline%20your%20criteria%2C%20you%20have%20to%20determine%20the%20impact.%20Map%20out%20what%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20side%20hustle%20will%20entail%20on%20every%20level%20and%20how%20it%20will%20impact%20your%20financial%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20Jean-Baptiste%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3Bdetermine%20the%20skill%20set%20required%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20what%20you%20are%20offering%2C%20how%20convenient%20will%20it%20be%20for%20you%20to%20do%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20monetary%2