0any%20kind.%20In%20fact%2C%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20plug%20an%20extension%20cord%20into%20the%20side%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20and%20it%20starts%20charging%20immediately.%20Even%20more%20exciting%2C%20the%20battery%20is%20in%20a%20chamber%20that%20keeps%20out%20water%20and%20dirt%2C%20so%20you%20can%20actually%20clean%20the%20riding%20mower%20with%20a%20hose%20and%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20any%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20comfortable%20seat%20and%20a%20deck%20where%20you%20can%20extend%20your%20legs%2C%20this%20riding%20lawn%20mower%20has%20a%20USB%20port%20in%20the%20onboard%20storage%20container%20to%20charge%20your%20phone%20as%20you%20mow.%20I%20particularly%20like%20how%20the%20LED%20headlights%20along%20the%20front%20and%20the%20sides%20light%20up%20the%20path%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20this%20lawn%20mower%20requires%20little%20maintenance%3A%20you%20won't%20ever%20have%20to%20change%20engine%20oil%2C%20spark%20plugs%2C%20an%20air%20filter%2C%20or%20mower%20belt%20with%20the%20John%20Deere%20Z370R%20Electric%20ZTrak%20Mower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20small%20yards%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20small%20yards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sun%20Joe%20MJ401C-PRO%20electric%20lawn%20mower%20may%20not%20have%20the%20width%20to%20be%20a%20practical%20option%20for%20larger%20yards%2C%20but%20its%20compact%20design%20and%20battery%20power%20make%20it%20ideal%20for%20small%20or%20medium-sized%20ones.%20You%20can%20mow%20up%20to%20a%20quarter%20acre%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%20The%20relatively%20narrow%20width%20also%20makes%20it%20convenient%20to%20maneuver%20around%20tight%20landscaping%20elements%20like%20rocks%20or%20other%20obstacles%20that%20require%20more%20precision%20than%20a%20larger%20mower%20offers.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20the%20Sun%20Joe%20for%20this%20list%20because%20I%20appreciate%20anything%20that%20improves%20operation%20safety%2C%20especially%20la