3EThriving%20Yard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20own%20hands-on%20experience%20with%20various%20brands%2C%20we%20assembled%20this%20list%20of%20the%20best%20electric%20mowers%20you%20can%20buy.%20We%20also%20used%20our%20experience%20with%20large%20power%20tools%20to%20help%20evaluate%20battery%20life%2C%20runtimes%2C%20and%20power%20output.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we%20did%20not%20test%20all%20the%20options%20we%20chose%2C%20we%20reviewed%20owner%20and%20operation%20manuals%2C%20watched%20online%20tutorials%2C%20and%20consulted%20with%20lawn%20care%20equipment%20expert%20to%20develop%20our%20categories%20For%20models%20we%20did%20test%2C%20we%20used%20them%20on%20a%20half-acre%20yard%20a%20few%20times%20to%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20cutting%20capabilities%2C%20self%20propel%20features%2C%20deck%20size%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20also%20used%20a%20set%20of%20specific%20criteria%20to%20help%20us%20evaluate%20and%20compare%20potential%20options%20and%20what%20to%20look%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20Capacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20cordless%20options%2C%20we%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20Ah%20(amp%20hour)%20of%20the%20included%20battery.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20Ah%2C%20the%20more%20energy%20the%20battery%20can%20store%2C%20the%20higher%20power%20output%2C%20and%20the%20longer%20it%20will%20last.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharging%20Time%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20recharge%20a%20depleted%20battery%20can%20seriously%20affect%20the%20convenience%20of%20a%20cordless%20mower.%20If%20your%20battery%20can%20be%20recharged%20quickly%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20get%20back%20to%20work%20soon%2C%20and%20there's%20less%20of%20a%20chance%20that%20you'll%20need%20to%20purchase%20a%20second%20battery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERuntime%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOverall%20runtime%20per%20battery%20charge%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20important%20metric%20to%20consider%20when%20evaluating%20cordless%20mowers%20%E2%80%94%20obviously%2C%20corded%20models%20will%20provide%20the%20longest.%20The%20longer%20the%20runtime%2C%20the%20better%2C%20especially%20for%20larger%20mowers%20that%20will%20be%20purchased%20to%20use%20on%20larger%20lawns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lighter%20the%20mower%20weighs%2C%20the%20less%20effort%20it%20will%20place%20on%20the%20battery%20and%20the%20longer%20the%20overall%20runtime.%20We%20did%20our%20best%20to%20choose%20lighter%20options%20whenever%20possible%20while%20still%20considering%20overall%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EElectric%20lawn%20mower%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20benefits%20of%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20lawn%20mowers%20are%20just%20as%20effective%20as%20gas-powered%20lawn%20mowers%20but%20without%20certain%20drawbacks.%20They%20don't%20require%20gas%20or%20oil%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20emit%20harmful%20fumes%20or%20exhaust%2C%20making%20them%20far%20more%20environmentally%20friendly.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20electric%20lawnmowers%20come%20with%20far%20less%20maintenance.%20You'll%20never%20have%20to%20change%20a%20spark%20plug%20(because%20they're%20not%20outfitted%20with%20them)%20or%20remove%20the%20oil%20and%20gas%20before%20you%20winterize%20the%20mower%20in%20the%20winter.%20They%20are%20also%20quieter%20in%20operation.%20While%20they%20may%20have%20a%20more%20expensive%20up-front%20cost%2C%20they%20will%20also%20be%20cheaper%20to%20operate%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20do%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%20last%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBattery-powered%20mowers%20themselves%20can%20last%20up%20to%2010%20years%2C%20but%20their%20batteries%20will%20only%20last%20about%204%20years%20before%20they're%20unable%20to%20hold%20an%20effective%20charge.%20To%20ensure%20your%20batteries%20will%20last%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20try%20to%20completely%20deplete%20the%20battery%20before%20recharging%20it.%20This%20will%20reduce%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20charging%20cycles%20placed%20on%20the%20battery%2C%20increasing%20its%20lifespan.%20You%20should%20also%20do%20your%20best%20to%20remove%20the%20battery%20from%20the%20charger%20once%20it's%20fully%20charged%3Cstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorded%20mowers%20have%20a%20similar%20lifespan%20as%20long%20as%20they're%20cared%20for%20properly.%20There%20are%20no%20batteries%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20but%20their%20extension%20cords%20are%20just%20as%20important%20to%20pay%20attention%20to.%20This%20means%20using%20the%20correct%20gauge%20for%20the%20job%2C%20which%20indicates%20how%20thick%20the%20cord%20is.%20The%20thicker%20the%20cord%2C%20the%20more%20voltage%20will%20reach%20the%20mower%20and%20the%20less%20unnecessary%20work%20the%20motor%20has%20to%20do.%20Your%20mower's%20operating%20manual%20should%20tell%20you%20the%20best%20gauge%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20expensive%20are%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20lawn%20mowers%20are%20available%20at%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20prices%2C%20although%20corded%20models%20tend%20to%20be%20cheaper%20than%20battery-powered%20options.%20Corded%20mowers%20also%20won't%20require%20any%20additional%20battery%20purchases%20over%20time.%20Size%20also%20plays%20a%20part.%20Large%20riding%20mowers%20can%20cost%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20while%20smaller%2C%20compact%20machines%2C%20like%20the%20Sun%20Joe%20MJ401C-PRO%2C%20our%20recommendation%20for%20small%20yards%2C%20can%20be%20found%20for%20about%20%24200.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20requires%20the%20fuel%20or%20oil%20that%20gas-powered%20models%20do%2C%20which%20should%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20overall%20expense%20of%20the%20mower.%20However%2C%20the%20long-term%20cost%20of%20replacement%20batteries%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%