20land%2C%20including%20rice%2C%20cucumbers%20and%20pumpkins%2C%20we%20sold%20them%20at%20a%20local%20market%20in%20Imphal.%20We%20would%20walk%204%20km%20and%20catch%20the%20bus%20to%20Imphal.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20her%20but%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20feed%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20there%20was%20an%20elderly%20lady%20at%20the%20market%2C%20probably%20a%20vegetable%20wholesaler%20or%20trader%2C%20who%20regularly%20saw%20Neisem%20(Chungreng%E2%80%99s%20mother)%20at%20the%20market%20and%20heard%20about%20how%20she%20was%20struggling%20financially.%20Barely%20a%20young%20boy%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20remembers%20what%20happens%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20when%20we%20came%20to%20the%20market%2C%20that%20elderly%20lady%20approached%20my%20mother%20saying%20that%20her%20daughter%20was%20a%20wrestling%20coach%20at%20the%20Special%20Areas%20Games%20(SAG)%20centre%20run%20by%20the%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(SAI)%20in%20the%20Khuman%20Lampak%20area%20of%20Imphal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20their%20conversation%2C%20my%20mother%20talked%20about%20losing%20her%20husband%20and%20the%20financial%20struggles%20at%20home.%20My%20mother%20also%20said%20that%20she%20had%20three%20sons%2C%20and%20if%20her%20%5Belderly%20lady%E2%80%99s%5D%20daughter%20could%20coach%20one%20of%20them%2C%20she%20would%20be%20very%20grateful.%20Soon%2C%20a%20wrestling%20coach%20visited%20our%20home%2C%20took%20a%20look%20at%20me%20and%20agreed%20to%20coach%20me.%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20in%20wrestling%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20about%2012%20or%2013%20at%20the%20SAG%20centre%20in%20Khuman%20Lampak%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20struggling%20for%20a%20year%2C%20he%20developed%20a%20good%20understanding%20of%20wrestling%20and%20began%20competing%20in%20different%20age%20groups%20representing%20Manipur%20in%20regional%20tournaments.%20Chungreng%20aimed%20to%20one%20day%20represent%20India%20in%20the%20Olympics.%20Meanwhile%2C%20his%20mother%20was%20working%20in%20the%20fields%20back%20home%2C%20barely%20earning%20Rs%20150%20to%20Rs%20200%20a%20day%2C%20and%20his%20elder%20brothers%20found%20work%20operating%20JCBs%20far%20away%20up%20in%20the%20hills.%20Education%20was%20a%20luxury%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20to%20come%20back%20home%20and%20visit%20my%20family.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20money%20to%20travel%20for%20tournaments.%20There%20were%20times%20I%20would%20borrow%20money%20from%20my%20friends%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20return%20it.%20Despite%20getting%20selected%20to%20compete%20in%20national%20tournaments%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20money%20to%20travel.%20I%20remember%20juniors%20training%20with%20me%2C%20would%20talk%20behind%20my%20back%20saying%20that%20I%20was%20poor.%20I%20had%20aspirations%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261513%2Fpooja-rani-boxing-tokyo-olympics-sports-hero-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompeting%20in%20the%20Olympics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20despite%20progressing%20well%2C%20poverty%20came%20in%20the%20way.%20Whenever%20I%20think%20of%20these%20times%2C%20I%20start%20to%20cry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20with%20tears%20flowing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20wrestling%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20Chungreng%20decided%20that%20his%20time%20was%20better-spent%20farming%2C%20working%20as%20a%20farm%20hand%20on%20rice%20fields%20and%20supporting%20the%20family.%20By%20the%20middle%20of%202012%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20wrestling%20altogether%2C%20fell%20in%20love%2C%20got%20married%2C%20and%20went%20back%20home.%20About%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20his%20first%20child%20was%20born%2C%20and%20life%20seemed%20destined%20to%20go%20in%20a%20certain%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201032px)%20100vw%2C%201032px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manipur%20MMA%20Representative%20Chungreng%20Koren%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448.jpg%201032w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22581%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChungreng%20Koren%20laboured%20in%20the%20rice%20fields%20of%20Manipur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20night%2C%20however%2C%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20feeling%20struck%20me.%20At%20night%2C%20I%20would%20suddenly%20get%20the%20urge%20to%20do%20push-ups%20and%20other%20exercises.%20When%20my%20wife%20asked%20me%20what%20happened%2C%20I%20told%20her%20that%20I%20had%20a%20deep%20desire%20to%20compete%20in%20sports.%20Despite%20our%20financial%20situation%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20the%20urge%20to%20compete%20and%20it%20was%20bothering%20me%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20went%20on%20for%20about%20two%20months%20until%20he%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20confide%20in%20his%20mother%20as%20well.%20Chungreng%20told%20her%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20practise%20wrestling%20again%20and%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20with%20my%20life.%20In%20response%2C%20my%20mother%20said%20that%20since%20I%20had%20a%20wife%20and%20a%20child%2C%20how%20would%20I%20support%20them%20with%20no%20money%20coming%20in%20from%20wrestling%3F%20My%20mother%20also%20said%20that%20she%20was%20growing%20old%20and%20needed%20help%20running%20the%20household.%20This%20back%20and%20forth%20went%20on%20for%20a%20year%20until%20I%20told%20my%20mother%20that%20if%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20back%20to%20wrestling%2C%20I%20would%20lose%20my%20mind%20and%20that%20I%20wanted%20my%20child%20to%20play%20sports%20and%20have%20a%20chance%20at%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20changed%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20mind%20a%20little%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20it%20was%20a%20local%20pastor%20who%20convinced%20her%20to%20let%20him%20train%20again%20with%20the%20belief%20that%20it%20would%20amount%20to%20something%20better.%20In%202016%2C%20Chungreng%20came%20back%20to%20wrestling.%20To%20help%20chase%20his%20dream%2C%20his%20mother%20worked%20even%20harder%2C%20sold%20whatever%20she%20could%20grow%2C%20and%20found%20work%20in%20Imphal.%20The%20four%20of%20them%20(Chungreng%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20wife%20and%20child)%20moved%20to%20a%20one-room%20residence%20near%20the%20Khuman%20Lampak%20area.%20While%20he%20was%20training%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20construction%20labourer%20in%20the%20afternoon%20and%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chungreng%20Koren%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0016-1713277280-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347403%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChungreng%20Koren%20worked%20in%20construction%20to%20support%20his%20dreams%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20he%20qualified%20for%20the%20National%20Games%20competing%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%2072%20kg%20category.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20sponsor%20my%20travel%20and%20training%2C%20my%20mother%20went%20back%20to%20our%20village%20and%20collected%20money%20by%20asking%20everyone%20to%20contribute%20whatever%20amount%20they%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20National%20Games%20were%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Goa%20in%20November%202017%2C%20Chungreng%20decided%20to%20train%20at%20the%20SAI%20facility%20in%20Rohtak%2C%20Haryana.%20For%20a%20month%20before%20the%20event%2C%20he%20trained%20well%20but%20the%20event%20was%20postponed%20with%20no%20date%20in%20sight%20of%20when%20it%20was%20going%20to%20happen.%20It%20was%20a%20devastating%20blow.%20The%20next%20National%20Games%20would%20only%20take%20place%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manipur%20MMA%20legend%20Chungreng%20Koren%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-winning-a-fight-1713276544-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChungreng%20Koren%20overcame%20so%20much%20in%20life%20to%20become%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20standout%20MMA%20fighters%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMMA%20calling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20wrestling%20career%20not%20going%20anywhere%2C%20Chungreng%20decided%20to%20call%20Roshan%20Mainam%2C%20an%20MMA%20fighter%20from%20Manipur%20and%20an%20acquaintance%20from%20his%20first%20stint%20in%20wrestling.%20Following%20the%20National%20Games%20debacle%2C%20Chungreng%20told%20Roshan%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20train%20and%20compete%20in%20MMA%20because%20there%20was%20nothing%20else%20left%20for%20him.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20Roshan%20was%20trying%20out%20for%20Evolve%20MMA%2C%20a%20renowned%20Singapore-based%20gym%2C%20which%20produces%20fighters%20for%20ONE%20Championship%20%E2%80%94%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20most%20recognised%20MMA%20promotion%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20major%20promotions%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Roshan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20sometime%20in%202006%20at%20junior%20wrestling%20tournaments%20in%20Manipur%20although%20he%20was%20competing%20in%20a%20higher%20weight%20category.%20By%202018%2C%20as%20I%20was%20getting%20recognised%20for%20MMA%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20potential%20of%20making%20the%20switch%20from%20wrestling.%20After%20seeing%20the%20recognition%20I%20was%20getting%2C%20we%20got%20in%20touch.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20some%20success%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20my%20financial%20situation%20started%20to%20get%20better.%20In%20November%202018%2C%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20train%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Evolve%20MMA%20gym%20in%20Singapore.%20But%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20earlier%2C%20while%20I%20was%20training%20at%20Koi%20Combat%20Academy%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20invited%20Chungreng%20to%20come%20down%20and%20train%20there.%20Initially%2C%20I%20took%20care%20of%20all%20his%20expenses%20to%20train%20at%20the%20academy%20because%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20good%20place%20financially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRoshan%20invited%20me%20to%20train%20at%20Koi%20Combat%20Academy%20and%20trained%20me%20for%20about%20two%20months%20before%20leaving%20for%20Singapore%2C%20following%20which%20Vishal%20%5BSeigell%5D%20Sir%20took%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Chungreng.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20selection%20to%20Evolve%20MMA%2C%20Roshan%20signed%20a%20%2448%2C000-a-year%20contract%20for%20three%20years%20in%20which%20he%20would%20train%20full-time%20and%20compete%20in%20ONE%20Championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20I%20was%20training%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I%20was%20helping%20fighters%20like%20Chungreng%20who%20were%20struggling%20financially.%20The%20reason%20why%20I%20support%20fighters%20like%20him%20is%20because%20I%20come%20from%20similar%20circumstances.%20I%20grew%20up%20as%20a%20sickly%20child%20in%20a%20poor%20family%20with%20a%20chronically%20sick%20father%20and%20a%20mother%20who%20worked%20extremely%20hard%20at%20a%20rice%20mill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20to%20train%20when%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20to%20train%20in%20MMA%2C%20and%20thankfully%20had%20coaches%20there%20who%20supported%20me%20similarly.%20So%2C%20I%20promised%20to%20myself%20that%20if%20I%20ever%20earned%20any%20notoriety%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20I%20would%20help%20other%20fighters%20after%20me%20from%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20whatever%20support%20Roshan%20could%20offer%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20and%20Chungreng%20was%20still%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20When%20COVID-19%20struck%2C%20Chungreng%20left%20Bengaluru%20and%20his%20MMA%20dreams%20were%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance.%20But%20during%20the%20brief%20lull%20after%20the%20first%20wave%2C%20Roshan%20opened%20a%20gym%20in%20Imphal%20called%20RMX%20Mixed%20Martial%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%20where%20he%20took%20in%20Chungreng%20as%20a%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20time%20spent%20training%20in%20Bengaluru%20would%20also%20allow%20him%20to%20take%20on%2023%20amateur%20fights%20(all%20wins)%20and%20his%20first%20professional%20fight%20at%20the%20Warriors%20Fighting%20Championship%20(WFC)%2C%20a%20local%20promotion%2C%20in%20January%202020.%20It%20was%20a%20valuable%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-Koren-Training-MMA-1713276641.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chungreng%20is%20Manipur%20MMA's%20brightest%20s